snippet: U.S. defense officials said Thursday that Russia has pulled most of its forces away from the Ukraine border, a withdrawal that the U.S. has been demanding for weeks....

headline.print_headline: AP Sources: Russian Troops Leaving Ukraine Border
headline.main: AP Sources: Russian Troops Leaving Ukraine Border

lead_paragraph: U.S. defense officials said Thursday that Russia has pulled most of its forces away from the Ukraine border, a withdrawal that the U.S. has been demanding for weeks.
